channel.title: 'Server is already in use problem.' And another 1
channel.description:
Hey,
1.When i downloaded a server i try to make it online but everytime i do that, there stays 'Server is already in use.' (Or something like that)
2. I just iped myself at a server (lol) how do i unip myself?
Greetz,

item.title: 'Server is already in use problem.' And another 1
item.dc:creator: @Reithen Reithen
item.description:
@Reithen wrote:

[quote=“rash, post:5, topic:376874”][quote author=Reithen link=topic=472792.msg3457574#msg3457574 date=1294165662]

what server is it pi or delta?

What the fuck does that matter?

For your first problem, something is already using port 43593, probably utorrent.

for your second problem, check your ipban text file

Ty, going to use that. And utorrent is running on that port … Why do i need utorrent than?
By the way thanx for your help

,
[/quote]

Close Utorrent, run the server than run Utorrent again.

Your welcome[/quote]
You will be great if you know how i put my server online. I got no-ip and i got utorrent … I am so happy if you help me out.
Maybe you know a good video or a great tutorial?

Thx for your time anyway.
